snippet.title: Command and Conquer Gold: Intro Movie
snippet.description:
I will play the gold edition of CnC this time. Sometimes I use gameplay from the dos version aswell.  The NOD campaign is much harder. The first seven missions can be completed very fast and the others are not so easy.
Now sit back and enjoy the intro and the following NOD walkthrough of the RTS godfather that starts a new genre in video game history!
